🎓 Student Record Management System

---

📌 Project Title

Student Record Management System

---

📖 Problem Statement

Educational institutions often maintain student information manually using paper records or spreadsheets. This approach can result in data redundancy, record loss, difficulty in retrieving information, and increased administrative workload. The Student Record Management System provides a centralized platform for storing, managing, and accessing student records efficiently and accurately.

---

🎯 Project Objectives

- Maintain student records digitally and efficiently.
- Store personal, academic, and attendance information.
- Manage student data securely.
- Generate reports quickly and accurately.
- Reduce manual paperwork and human errors.
- Improve overall administrative productivity.

---

💻 Technologies Used

Front End

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

Back End

- Python (Flask / Django)

Database

- MySQL

---

🧩 System Modules

1. User Management

- User Login
- Authentication
- Role Management

2. Student Management

- Add Student
- Update Student Details
- Delete Student Records
- Search Student Information

3. Attendance Management

- Mark Attendance
- View Attendance Records

4. Academic Management

- Record Marks
- Calculate Grades
- Manage Results

5. Course Management

- Add Courses
- Assign Students to Courses

6. Report Generation

- Student Reports
- Attendance Reports
- Academic Performance Reports

---

🗄️ Database Design

User Table

Field Name| Data Type
user_id| INT
username| VARCHAR(50)
password| VARCHAR(255)
role| VARCHAR(20)

---

Student Table

Field Name| Data Type
student_id| INT
student_name| VARCHAR(100)
gender| VARCHAR(10)
date_of_birth| DATE
department| VARCHAR(100)
year| INT
phone_number| VARCHAR(15)
email| VARCHAR(100)

---

Attendance Table

Field Name| Data Type
attendance_id| INT
student_id| INT
attendance_date| DATE
status| VARCHAR(20)

---

Course Table

Field Name| Data Type
course_id| INT
course_name| VARCHAR(100)
department| VARCHAR(100)

---

Marks Table

Field Name| Data Type
mark_id| INT
student_id| INT
subject_name| VARCHAR(100)
marks| INT
grade| VARCHAR(5)

---

✅ Expected Outcome

The Student Record Management System will provide a centralized and efficient platform for managing student information, attendance records, academic performance, and course details. The system will improve data accuracy, enhance accessibility, reduce administrative workload, and support faster decision-making within educational institutions.

---

🏁 Conclusion

The Student Record Management System is designed to simplify and automate student data management processes. By integrating student records, attendance tracking, academic performance monitoring, and report generation into a single system, it improves efficiency, minimizes errors, and provides a reliable solution for educational institutions.

---

